# ABP — Project Standards

> **When to apply:** Attach when creating or modifying components, design tokens, `next.config.js`, or GitHub Actions workflow. Not needed for pure logic/utility work.

---

## Design Tokens (Source of Truth)

All values live in `styles/design-tokens.css`. **Never hardcode hex values or font names inline.**

| Token | Value |
|---|---|
| `--color-text` | `#52325b` |
| `--color-text-muted` | `#76547d` |
| `--color-primary` | `#7c2d86` |
| `--color-primary-hover` | `#682370` |
| `--color-card-surface` | `rgba(251, 247, 251, .78)` |
| `--color-border` | `rgba(84, 42, 90, 0.18)` |
| `--color-divider` | `rgba(84, 42, 90, 0.20)` |
| `--font-display` | `Cormorant Garamond, Georgia, serif` |
| `--font-body` | `Lexend, Arial, sans-serif` |
| `--font-heading-ui` | `Comic Relief, sans-serif` |
| `--font-micro` | `Atkinson Hyperlegible, sans-serif` |

**Font size floor:** never below `9px`. Micro/label minimum: `9.5px` (`var(--text-micro)`).
**Font weight floor:** `450` minimum everywhere; target `500`.

Background gradient: `linear-gradient(90deg, #f7f3f8 0%, #f0d8f1 55%, #d7b0dc 100%)`

