## AI Aesthetic — Never Do These

- Add more purple/violet gradients (design uses purple intentionally already)
- Center-align body text, cards, or feature descriptions
- Use icon-in-colored-circle feature grids
- Use gradient buttons — solid `var(--color-primary)` only
- Apply `transform` directly to `<svg>` or `<img>` — always wrap

